    {
      "id": "2c49ce39-8866-4707-a87c-178bd2eb7565",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "EDM has surfaced as an alternative to use DM techniques on large swaths of educational data. Due to the multimodality and complexity of educational data that is available today, creating effective models may require skills in DS and/or domain knowledge that is not accessible to everyone. Thus, it is imperative to find novel ways to extract meaningful features. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "2c49ce39-8866-4707-a87c-178bd2eb7565",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "02fef9f2-c5c2-47ee-a111-eb7788556c5e"
        },
        "created_time": "2024-07-31T19:43:00.000Z",
        "last_edited_time": "2024-07-31T19:45:00.000Z",
