    {
      "id": "66396042-2348-432e-95ef-72e740f6dadd",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Models used only consider tree-based or rules-based options for interpretability purposes. The results show that the AutoML based approach ended up surpassing other techniques in the task of prediction, which represents a positive aspect for non-expert users. No indication of early prediction.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
